name: Lewis Hall
directions:
On the 1st floor, as you enter the front doors, walk up to the elevators, turn left as you approach them. Down that hallway, you will see two gender neutral restrooms on the left hand side.
Alternatively, you can take the elevator to the 2nd floor. As you step out of the elevator, turn left and go down the hallway. It is a little twisty, but you will see two restrooms, room numbers 215 and 217. They are both accessible and gender neutral.
comment: You have to be a resident and swipe your KU ID at the front entrance to enter the building. However, if you knock, the desk assistant will often let you in.
